thread.title_full: GoMedigap reviewed by Sandra K. Barr

author: Sandra K. Barr
title: Sandra K. Barr
text: My experience was wonderful. My helper Annalin was the best and could not have done it without her. My anxiety was so high and she walked me through everything. She is one of the best people I have ever talked to. Told her over and over again how helpful she was to me. would not have wanted anyone else. she answered all my questions. Great person and you are lucky to have her..
